    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[675ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [900ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 15-20 min or until the lentils are tender, stirring occasionally – this is your<strong> 'Nduja & aubergine lentil stew</strong></p>",
