    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the 'Nduja aubergine & lentil stew<strong> </strong>is ready, stir through <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Set aside, with the lid on, for 2-3 min for the flavours to develop – this is your <strong>one pot</strong> <strong>spicy 'Nduja & aubergine lentil stew</strong></p>",
