    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the <strong>halved ciabatta </strong>in the<strong> toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Once the ciabatta is toasted, rub the sliced-side of the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>over it (not a fan of raw garlic? Only use a little!)</p><p>Spread a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over the toasted ciabatta – this is your <strong>garlicky toast</strong></p>",
