      "instruction": "<p>Tear your <strong>basil</strong> over the <strong>one pot</strong> <strong>spicy 'Nduja & aubergine lentil stew </strong>and top with the<strong> remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>garlicky toast </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
